@yalx

> В браузере MS Edge, при включенном AdGuard не загружаются некоторые сайты. В Firefox плагин AdGuard работает корректно.

От настроек зависит?

@Bushido1 Hi!
Unfortunately, I cannot reproduce this issue. 
Please disable filter lists one by one, if you find which one causes that issue, then please re-enable it, open filterling log, reproduce issue, make a screenshot of filtering log with all blocked requests/elements and upload it here.
